{"tid":819614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[山竹] 政府籲撤離 大澳廢老不願走","createTime":"2018-09-15T03:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T16:35:29.000Z","uid":62063,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"126fe11454baa8dc5ae77b9861d9652f897d4f6b","tid":819614,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180915/s00001/1536949244740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180915%2Fs00001%2F1536949244740&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a17f2cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180915%2Fs00001%2F1536949244740&h=6e8d4062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180915/s00001/1536949244740</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】超強颱風山竹來臨在即，大澳商戶紛紛採取防風措施，如將電器架高、加裝防水閘等，務求將損失減至最低。民政署呼籲位於低窪地區的棚屋居民盡早撤離，不過，有年邁居民坦言，會留守家園。<br />\n<br />\n大澳鄉事委員會主席劉焯榮表示，棚屋住的大部分是長者，擔心棚屋無法承受風力，山竹吹襲時會引起骨牌效應，一連串的棚屋被吹走。離島民政事務署人員昨日到低窪地區，呼籲居民於3號強風信號懸掛時，撤離至防風庇護站，屆時亦會有旅遊巴接送居民。劉指，鄉委會於周三已發出緊急通告，呼籲居民做好防風措施，另外亦設立了3個防風庇護站，惟3處合共只能提供不足40個牀鋪。<br />\n<br />\n不少居民縱然收到民政署的撤離呼籲，但仍堅持於颱風吹襲期間留守家園。獨居的馮伯表示，居住大澳多年，未曾於颱風期間撤離，<span style=\"color: red;\">他坦言即便山竹來襲，也要守住家園</span>。馮曾三度中風，去年「天鴿」襲港，其電動輪椅被浸壞，昨日有消防員到場，為他架高電動輪椅。<br />\n<br />\n年逾八十的冼婆婆坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\">即便知道家園靠近海邊，但她依然相信家園十分安全</span>。她又指，除非女兒來接走自己，否則她不會離開大澳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b9b8ddde603837807e93fad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b9b8ddde603837807e93fad&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=73971860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b9b8ddde603837807e93fad</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大澳居民莊婆婆稱：「到時有橡皮艇有警察，一打電話就有警察。」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/110241_0bdc4ec501ed997feed88e7b79d8c784.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F110241_0bdc4ec501ed997feed88e7b79d8c784.png&h=47129428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/110245_ad1d1e02945a4fc3705f975b7217a584.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F110245_ad1d1e02945a4fc3705f975b7217a584.png&h=581a01af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(好彩有返啲正常人)<br />\n大澳居民方婆婆說：「會離開，就算會游泳都會淹死，你夠不夠那些浪來，夠不夠那些水？到時放棄了，走就走，沒有辦法。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/110354_3fa5cbf8ca5487b7bd8f7eaaefaac94b.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F110354_3fa5cbf8ca5487b7bd8f7eaaefaac94b.PNG&h=c2c135fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/110359_d3e4d756b064675c57f51ed6415b2c6a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F110359_d3e4d756b064675c57f51ed6415b2c6a.PNG&h=803fe365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae5fd5f19a2d59b45833365b799a5ddf4cc637ef","tid":819614,"uid":191815,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"迫佢簽生死狀仲睇下佢留唔留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849b9e810f73177ee99dcd6d5c75739d01de2838","tid":819614,"uid":42667,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"廢老又要害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48bbbfedc4c1145f8512355ca34aafbdec3c4e8","tid":819614,"uid":204728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:08:14.000Z","msg":"死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":